reviewText: Love Luke Bryan's music but wanted to learn more about him.  He seems like such a nice guy and so down to earth.  The DVD confirms that.  It was nice to hear his story and how he became so famous.  Oh and Zac Brown, quit being a bully and keep your opinions to yourself.
